```
|------------------|----------------|---------------|----------------|--------------|
| ...              | ...            | ...           | ...            | ...          |
| Paid-in Capital  | 28000000.00    | 2023-12-31    | 28000000.00    | 2024-02-05   |
| ...              | ...            | ...           | ...            | ...          |
```

1. **Initial Value of Paid-in Capital**: 
   - The initial value on '2023-12-31' is **28,000,000.00**.

2. **End Value of Paid-in Capital**: 
   - The end value on '2024-02-05' is **28,000,000.00**.
